f_{X_\frac{T}{K}}(x)= \frac{e^{-\frac{\lambda T}{K}\left(\frac{\lambda T}{K}\right)^x}}{x!}
f_T(t)= \lambda e^{-\lambda t}
Cov(X,T)=0
E(XT)=E(X)E(T)=\left(\frac{\lambda T}{K}\right)\left(\frac{1}{\lambda}\right)=\frac{T}{K}
E[T^2] = \frac{2}{\lambda^2}
   E\left\{ N\left(\frac{T}{K} \right) T\right\} = E\left\{ E \left[ N\left(\frac{T}{K} \right) \mid T \right] T\right\} = E\left\{  \left(\frac{\lambda T}{K} \right)  T \right\} = \frac{\lambda}{K} E[ T^2 ] = \frac{2}{\lambda K}. 
